🔹 Procedure Question

❓ Write a stored procedure to accept value of n and display first n even numbers.


---

✅ Procedure

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE even_numbers(n INT)
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $$
DECLARE
    i INT := 2;
    count INT := 0;
BEGIN
    WHILE count < n LOOP
        RAISE NOTICE '%', i;
        i := i + 2;
        count := count + 1;
    END LOOP;
END;
$$;


---

✅ Call

CALL even_numbers(10);


